    "Polyp segmentation is already a challenging domain because there is a limited review of the existing problems that includes a comparison analysis of retrieved publications.",
    "Most of the review papers on polyps do not properly explain the segmentation techniques in terms of the models and the available datasets on polyps.",
    "Some of the review studies discussed the endoscopy domain and some of the papers only represent the summarized study which does not show any significant understanding of polyp.",
